  "title": "Chief Academic Director",
  "description": "<ul><li>Interview, recruit and train teachers.</li><li>Select student and teacher of the month awards.</li><li>Plan staff meetings, orientations, trainings and workshops.</li><li>Support and participate in college and community related activities.</li><li>Develop educational process and policies to meet curriculum goals.</li><li>Develop curriculum goals for students at different grades.</li><li>Provide training to faculty on latest instructional technology and technique.</li><li>Develop unique and interactive educational programs and courses for students.</li><li>Develop and implement teaching staff development programs</li><li>Develop and implement academic enhancement programs for students.</li><li>Plan and schedule regular assessements for students</li><li>Prepare students' assessments feedback and meet up with the parents</li><li>Order and stock books and other school supplies as needed</li></ul>",
